<h1><img src="img/af_icon2.png" alt="Ansifilter Logo">Ansifilter 2.10</h1>

	<b>Ansifilter</b> handles text files containing ANSI terminal escape codes.
	<ul>
	<li>Command sequences may be stripped or interpreted</li>
	<li>Coloured output in HTML, LaTeX, TeX, RTF and BBCode format</li>
	<li>Converts ANSI art (Codepage437, BIN, XBIN, Tundra) to HTML or RTF</li>
	<li>Enables &quot;tail -f&quot; functionality on Windows</li>
	<li>CLI and GUI builds</li>
	<li>Available for Linux/Mac/Windows</li>	
	</ul>

