<b>MikroLock</b> reads and writes encrypted miniLock files.
<ul>
	<li>No cumbersome key exchange</li>
	<li>Easy handling - no nerd assistance required</li>
	<li>Compatible to original Chrome plugin (minilock.io)</li>
	<li>...but can also handle big files</li>
	<li>Uses Scrypt or Argon2 for key derivation, XSalsa20 for encryption, Blake2 for verification</li>
	<li>CLI, GUI and Lib builds</li>
	<li>Available for Linux/Windows</li>
</ul>

